g.aria-label: Go the Way of the Deer until you've passed the sign of an animal, then go the Way of that animal for a block. If you reach the end of the neighborhood without passing the sign of an animal, make a U-turn and keep trying. Choose a direction and drive straight, stopping immediately after passing an orange sign that you have not yet passed. Choose the direction such that you drive the fewest blocks doing this. Turn left or right -- whichever points towards the center of the neighborhood -- and drive two blocks forward.
